Sinatrails is sinatra bootstrap project that suit to my needs to create web application with Rails-like directory structure, Active Record as ORM, and jQuery.

To use this project:
1. git clone git://github.com/kuntoaji/sinatrails.git
2. bundle install
3. run rake db:create to create database
4. run rake db:migrate to run migration
5. run rake populate_dummy to create dummy users.
6. run ./scripts/test to run all test units.
7. ./scripts/server -s thin to execute the thin server or ./scripts/console to the console.

